        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2224000029" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14851957452880200444">Oh, Ramona. Kindergarten drop-out with a doll named Chevrolet and singing about the dawnzer lee light, you hold up to my memories. I cannot believe how long ago this was written because it really does not feel dated, other than in a few small instances that are easily forgiven. Beverly Cleary was ahead of her time, and Ramona is a timeless character.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


